  "prompt": "What are the 5 best Cirque du Soleil songs and from which show do they come?",
  "response": "Cirque du Soleil is renowned for its enchanting performances, many of which are underscored by memorable music. While tastes and opinions vary, here are five songs that are often cited as some of the best from various shows:\n\n1. **\"Alegr\u00eda\" from *Alegr\u00eda*** - This song is iconic and embodies the spirit of the show with its emotional and powerful melody.\n2. **\"K\u00e0 The Battle\" from *K\u00e0*** - This song combines epic orchestration with intense rhythms, perfectly mirroring the show's dramatic and thrilling performances.\n3. **\"Mirko\" from *Varekai*** - Known for its haunting beauty, this song captures the ethereal and mystical ambiance of the show.\n4. **\"O\" from *O*** - The aquatic-themed song echoes the timeless and surreal nature of this water-centric performance.\n5. **\"Butterfly\" from *Quidam*** - This song is poignant and evocative, resonating deeply with the themes of loss and discovery in the show.\n\nThese selections showcase the diversity and emotional depth of Cirque du Soleil's music, adding to the overall magical experience of their performances.",
